Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.13,0:00:07.22,Default,,0,0,0,,个人日志，星历3013.1\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Personal log, stardate 3013.1.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.85,0:00:11.39,Default,,0,0,0,,过去24小时发生的事让我难以置信\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I find it hard to believe the events of the past 24 hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.56,0:00:14.85,Default,,0,0,0,,史波克在军事法庭的申述也让人难以置信\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Or the plea of Mr. Spock, standing general court-martial.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.02,0:00:16.27,Default,,0,0,0,,对于非法夺取星舰指挥权\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}How do you plead to the charge
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.44,0:00:18.56,Default,,0,0,0,,你认罪吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}of unlawfully taking command of this starship?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.73,0:00:20.07,Default,,0,0,0,,认罪\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Guilty.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.23,0:00:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,蓄意破坏星舰电脑系统\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Of sabotaging the computers of this vessel
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.53,0:00:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,,锁定航线，执意前往塔罗斯4号星球？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and locking it on a course for planet Talos IV?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.91,0:00:28.49,Default,,0,0,0,,- 认罪 - 劫持派克舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Guilty. - And of forcibly attempting to transport
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.66,0:00:31.91,Default,,0,0,0,,- 试图将其送至那颗星球？ - 认罪\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Captain Pike to that planet? - Guilty.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.08,0:00:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么？为什么史波克想要把他的前任舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Why? Why does Spock want to take to that forbidden world
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.71,0:00:39.33,Default,,0,0,0,,带到那个禁区？这位刚在空间事故中受了重伤\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}his former captain, mutilated by a recent space disaster,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.50,0:00:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,现在不成人形，不能说话不能行动的舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}now a shell of a man, unable to speak or move?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.34,0:00:47.22,Default,,0,0,0,,史波克给出的唯一答案就在听审室的屏幕上\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The only answer Spock would give was on the hearing-room screen.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.39,0:00:49.93,Default,,0,0,0,,至于这是如何做到的，他拒绝予以解释\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}How Spock could do this, he refused to explain.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.10,0:00:55.27,Default,,0,0,0,,但13年前的真实影像，就在我们眼前\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But there, before our eyes, actual images from 13 years ago
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.73,0:00:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,记录了当年的派克舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}of Captain Pike as he was when he commanded this vessel,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.94,0:01:01.11,Default,,0,0,0,,和那时的史波克\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}of Spock in those days,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.69,0:01:05.74,Default,,0,0,0,,以及进取号如何成为至今唯一\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and of how the Enterprise had become the first and only starship
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.90,0:01:08.53,Default,,0,0,0,,到达过塔罗斯4号星球的星舰\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}to visit Talos IV.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.95,0:01:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,他们收到从那颗星球发出的遇难信号\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They had received a distress signal from that planet
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.29,0:01:16.25,Default,,0,0,0,,并在那发现多年前失踪飞船的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and discovered there, still alive after many years,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.41,0:01:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,幸存者\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}the survivors of a missing vessel,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.42,0:01:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,但这一切全是幻觉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}only to find it was all an illusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.55,0:01:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,没有幸存者，没有营地\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No survivors. No encampment.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.88,0:01:28.55,Default,,0,0,0,,全是一个陷阱\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It was all a trap,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.72,0:01:30.97,Default,,0,0,0,,布陷阱的，是一种会制造幻觉的生物\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}set by a race of beings who could make a man believe
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.14,0:01:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,,它们制造的幻觉能以假乱真\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}he was seeing anything they wished him to see.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.22,0:01:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,它们抓走了派克舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And Captain Pike was gone,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.77,0:01:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,,出于何种目的，还不知晓\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}a prisoner for some unknown purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.81,0:01:42.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我们看的这些影像…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Then the images we've been seeing--
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.48,0:01:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,是从塔罗斯4号星球传来的，长官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Are coming from Talos IV, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.65,0:01:48.99,Default,,0,0,0,,史波克先生，你了解关于跟塔罗斯4号星球接触的准则\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Mr. Spock, you're aware of the orders regarding any contact with Talos IV.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.16,0:01:51.91,Default,,0,0,0,,你蓄意触犯了死刑\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You have deliberately invited the death penalty.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.20,0:01:58.29,Default,,0,0,0,,你明白你在干什么吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Do you know what you're doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.46,0:02:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你疯了吗？ - 舰长…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Have you lost your mind? - Captain...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.17,0:02:03.79,Default,,0,0,0,,吉姆，求你，不要阻止我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Jim, please don't stop me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.96,0:02:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,不要让他阻止我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Don't let him stop me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.17,0:02:09.01,Default,,0,0,0,,这关系到你的前途和派克舰长的生命\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's your career and Captain Pike's life.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.47,0:02:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你必须观看信息的后半部分\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You must see the rest of the transmission.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.36,0:02:26.61,Default,,0,0,0,,宇宙，最后的边疆\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Space, the final frontier.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.44,0:02:31.07,Default,,0,0,0,,这是星舰进取号的航程\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}These are the voyages Of the starship Enterprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.24,0:02:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,它的五年任务，是去探索未知的新世界\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Its five-year mission: To explore strange new worlds,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.24,0:02:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,找寻新的生命与新的文明\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}to seek out new life and new civilizations,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.12,0:02:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,勇敢地航向前人未至之境\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}to boldly go where no man has gone before.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.10,0:02:51.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H00FFFF&}TLF荣誉出品\N本字幕仅供学习交流，严禁用于商业途径{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.44,0:02:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H00FFFF&}-=TLF字幕组=-\N翻译：刘诗濛 傻得雷\N校对：kmdangdangli xjCGI{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.84,0:03:18.13,Default,,0,0,0,,困兽之斗（下）
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.16,0:03:22.06,Default,,0,0,0,,审判史波克的军事法庭在封闭的空间中进行\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The court-martial of Mr. Spock has been convened in closed session.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.55,0:03:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,不论我们如何防范\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Despite all we can do,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.38,0:03:28.30,Default,,0,0,0,,影像还是不停从塔罗斯4号星球传来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}images continue to be transmitted to us from Talos IV.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.47,0:03:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,星际舰队要求任何人不能和塔罗斯4号接触\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Starfleet has ordered no contact with Talos IV.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.89,0:03:33.31,Default,,0,0,0,,没有例外\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They made no exceptions.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.48,0:03:36.73,Default,,0,0,0,,你别无选择，长官，抱歉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You have no choice, sir. I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.15,0:03:41.65,Default,,0,0,0,,管理员已经控制了我们的屏幕\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The Keeper has taken over control of our screen.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.07,0:03:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,你明白吗，长官？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Do you understand, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.70,0:03:47.11,Default,,0,0,0,,正如你们之前所见\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}As you saw before,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.28,0:03:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,派克舰长被击晕之后\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Captain Pike had been knocked unconscious
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.45,0:03:51.70,Default,,0,0,0,,又被塔罗斯人抓走\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and captured by the Talosians.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.01,0:04:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,能听见吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Can you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.55,0:04:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我是克里斯托弗·派克\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}My name is Christopher Pike,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.97,0:04:51.30,Default,,0,0,0,,星际舰队进取号的指挥官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}commander of the space vehicle Enterprise from a stellar group
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.47,0:04:53.14,Default,,0,0,0,,来自银河系的另一端\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}at the other end of this galaxy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.14,0:04:56.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我们是为和平而来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Our intentions are peaceful.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.44,0:04:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,,你能明白吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Can you understand me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.90,0:05:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,看起来，治安官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It appears, magistrate,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.61,0:05:04.65,Default,,0,0,0,,这个样本的智力水平惊人得有限\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}that the intelligence of the specimen is shockingly limited.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.82,0:05:07.65,Default,,0,0,0,,这不奇怪，他的飞船不是轻易就被一条模拟信号\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}This is no surprise, since his vessel was baited here so easily
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.82,0:05:09.66,Default,,0,0,0,,给骗了过来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}with a simulated message.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.91,0:05:11.37,Default,,0,0,0,,读他的心思，就知道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}As you can read in its thoughts,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.53,0:05:13.91,Default,,0,0,0,,他现在才开始怀疑那些幸存者\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}it is only now beginning to suspect that the survivors
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.08,0:05:17.29,Default,,0,0,0,,和营地只是我们在他们大脑里制造的幻觉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and encampment were a simple illusion we placed in their minds.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.46,0:05:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,你没有说话，我却能听见你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You're not speaking, yet I can hear you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.54,0:05:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,你可以把这解释成我们思维的交换\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You will note the confusion as it reads our thought transmissions.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.17,0:05:24.75,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧，就是心灵感应\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}All right then, telepathy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.92,0:05:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,你们能读懂我的心思，我也能读懂你们的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You can read my mind, I can read yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.80,0:05:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,除非你们想让我的船员认为把我抓起来是出于恶意\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Unless you want my ship to consider capturing me an unfriendly act--
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.84,0:05:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,,现在看到的便是原始的“因害怕而威胁”的反应\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You'll now see the primitive fear-threat reaction.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.35,0:05:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,标本马上就会开始吹嘘他的能力\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The specimen is about to boast of his strength,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.81,0:05:40.27,Default,,0,0,0,,他飞船的武器\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}the weaponry of his vessel,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.77,0:05:42.15,Default,,0,0,0,,等等之类\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and so on.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.31,0:05:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,下面\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Next,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.52,0:05:47.11,Default,,0,0,0,,他因为挫败而开始使用他的体力\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}frustrated into a need to display physical prowess,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.28,0:05:50.21,Default,,0,0,0,,他会用自己的身体撞击透明壁障\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}the creature will throw himself against the transparency.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.41,0:06:00.83,Default,,0,0,0,,换做是你，难道就不想试试这墙有多牢吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}If you were in here, wouldn't you test the strength of these walls too?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.00,0:06:03.75,Default,,0,0,0,,肯定有办法出去，我会找到的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}There's a way out of any cage, and I'll find it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.92,0:06:06.55,Default,,0,0,0,,尽管受挫，这种生物似乎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Despite its frustration, the creature appears more adaptable
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.71,0:06:09.22,Default,,0,0,0,,拥有比其他星球标本更强的适应能力\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}than our specimens from other planets.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.38,0:06:11.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我们很快就可以开始实验了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We can soon begin the experiment.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.22,0:06:19.06,Default,,0,0,0,,这颗星球的居民住在地下\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The inhabitants of this planet must live deep underground,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.23,0:06:22.48,Default,,0,0,0,,也许还会生产食物和别的东西\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}probably manufacture food and other needs down there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.11,0:06:25.15,Default,,0,0,0,,测试表明星球的表面\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Now, our tests indicate the planet surface,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.32,0:06:27.86,Default,,0,0,0,,植被稀少，动物也很少见\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}without considerably more vegetation or some animals,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.03,0:06:29.69,Default,,0,0,0,,极度贫瘠，根本不适合生物的繁衍\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}is simply too barren to support life.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.90,0:06:32.66,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我们看到的幸存者只是脑中的幻象，史波克先生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}So we just thought we saw survivors there, Mr. Spock.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.82,0:06:36.87,Default,,0,0,0,,正是，这颗星球的生物给我们制造的幻觉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Exactly. An illusion, placed in our minds by this planet's inhabitants.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.04,0:06:38.91,Default,,0,0,0,,完美幻觉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It was a perfect illusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.08,0:06:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,他们让我们看到我们想看的一切\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They had us seeing just what we wanted to see:
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.12,0:06:45.33,Default,,0,0,0,,人类勇敢而让人敬佩的幸存者\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Human beings who'd survived with dignity and bravery.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.50,0:06:48.38,Default,,0,0,0,,一切都合乎逻辑，从营地的建筑\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Everything entirely logical, right down to the building of the camp,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.55,0:06:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,褴褛的衣服，所有一切\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}the tattered clothing, everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.30,0:06:55.43,Default,,0,0,0,,现在我们必须清楚这次行动的危险性\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Now, let's be sure we understand the danger of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.60,0:06:57.97,Default,,0,0,0,,这个星球的居民能读懂我们的心思\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The inhabitants of this planet can read our minds.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.14,0:07:01.31,Default,,0,0,0,,他们会根据对方所想，创造幻觉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They can create illusions out of a person's own thoughts,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.48,0:07:05.56,Default,,0,0,0,,记忆和经历，甚至欲望\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}memories and experiences, even out of a person's own desires.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.73,0:07:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,这些幻觉能跟这张桌面一样真实\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Illusions just as real and solid as this tabletop,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.53,0:07:10.19,Default,,0,0,0,,让人难辨真伪\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and just as impossible to ignore.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.36,0:07:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,他们抓走了派克舰长，他需要帮助\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's Captain Pike they've got. He needs help.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.53,0:07:15.41,Default,,0,0,0,,只要我们一靠近\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}If we start buzzing about down there,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.57,0:07:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我们可能会发现他们强大的精神力量\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}we're liable to find their mental power is so great,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.33,0:07:20.95,Default,,0,0,0,,足以将我们的飞船像苍蝇一样打落\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}they could reach out and swat this ship as though it were a fly.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.12,0:07:23.33,Default,,0,0,0,,激光手枪可能无法将门打破\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Now, that entry may have stood up against hand lasers,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.50,0:07:25.46,Default,,0,0,0,,但我们可以用飞船的能量来攻击它\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}but we can transmit the ship's power against it,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.63,0:07:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,足以炸毁半个大陆\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}enough to blast half a continent.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.26,0:07:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,轮机室负责传输飞船的能量\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Engineering deck will rig to transmit ship's power.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.18,0:07:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我们便能尝试把那块金属炸穿\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We'll try blasting through that metal.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.18,0:07:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我们对这个生物的思维进行了无数测试，治安官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Thousands of us are already probing the creature's thoughts, magistrate.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.06,0:07:50.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我们发现他有极好的记忆能力\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We find excellent memory capacity.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.07,0:07:53.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我感知到他对最近的一次生死决斗记忆最为强烈\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I read most strongly a recent death struggle
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.65,0:07:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,记忆中，他为自己的生命而战\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}in which it fought to protect its life.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.82,0:07:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,就从这个记忆开始\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We will begin with this,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.95,0:08:02.83,Default,,0,0,0,,给这个标本一些更有意思的东西去保护\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}giving the specimen something more interesting to protect.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.60,0:08:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,快，我们必须藏起来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Come on. We must hide ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.56,0:08:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,快，快\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Come. Come.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.36,0:08:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,快啊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.19,0:08:34.53,Default,,0,0,0,,那儿没人，没准有武器和食物\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's deserted. There'll be weapons and perhaps food.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.24,0:08:36.65,Default,,0,0,0,,这里是参宿七星球\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}This is Rigel VII.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.70,0:08:39.95,Default,,0,0,0,,求你了，我们必须藏起来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Please, we must hide ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.12,0:08:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我被关在笼子里，一个监狱，就像动物园\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I was in a cage, a cell, in some kind of a zoo.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.04,0:08:47.67,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我肯定还在原地 - 快啊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- I must still be there. - Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.83,0:08:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,他们进了我的思维\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They've reached into my mind
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.50,0:08:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,借助我的记忆，让我重返旧地\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and taken the memory of somewhere I've been.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.05,0:08:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,克莱人！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The Kaylar!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.17,0:08:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,和两周前发生的事情一模一样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's starting just as it happened two weeks ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.64,0:09:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,除了你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Except for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.19,0:09:14.65,Default,,0,0,0,,派克舰长出色的推理，各位\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}A brilliant deduction by Captain Pike, gentlemen.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.82,0:09:16.99,Default,,0,0,0,,是的，他的确还在牢房里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yes, he was still inside his cell.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.15,0:09:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,- 但也无能为力 - 那些塔罗斯人控制了他的大脑\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- But knowing that couldn't help him. - The Talosians controlled his brain.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.03,0:09:23.74,Default,,0,0,0,,把他带到任何地点，任何时间\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And could make him live any place, any time,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.91,0:09:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,任何他们设置的场景\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}any situation they wished.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.95,0:09:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,他能看见，能感觉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He would see, taste,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.08,0:09:31.71,Default,,0,0,0,,经历真实的遭遇，就像各位坐在这里一样真实\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}suffer, with the same reality as you gentlemen sitting there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.88,0:09:35.09,Default,,0,0,0,,头发长了，不一样的衣服，但的确是你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Longer hair, different dress, but it is you,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.26,0:09:37.59,Default,,0,0,0,,那位名叫维娜的幸存者\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}the one the survivors call Vina.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.76,0:09:42.47,Default,,0,0,0,,或者说，维娜的幻象，但是为什么又是你？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Or rather, the image of Vina. But why you again?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.64,0:09:45.31,Default,,0,0,0,,他们为什么不创造另一个女孩？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Why didn't they create a different girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.73,0:09:59.28,Default,,0,0,0,,快，如果你趁它不注意的时候攻击…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Quick. lf you attack while it's not looking...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.45,0:10:01.66,Default,,0,0,0,,但这只是一个梦\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But it's only a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.79,0:10:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,你必须杀掉他，就像你之前一样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You have to kill him, as you did here before.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.67,0:10:13.67,Default,,0,0,0,,你去和看守讲，我是不会照做的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You can tell my jailers I won't go along with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.84,0:10:15.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我不是为了获得晚餐而表演的动物\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm not an animal performing for its supper.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.84,0:10:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,不论你怎么说，你能感受一切，这才是关键\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It doesn't matter what you call this. You'll feel it. That's what matters.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.13,0:10:22.47,Default,,0,0,0,,你可以感受每一刻所发生的一切\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You'll feel every moment of whatever happens to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.29,0:12:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,结束了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.93,0:12:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,她是谁？他们为什么停止传输影像了？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Who is she? Why have they stopped the images?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.77,0:12:37.02,Default,,0,0,0,,因为他们知道派克舰长累了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Because they know that Captain Pike is fatigued.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.19,0:12:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我们一会儿再继续\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We can reconvene later.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.06,0:12:40.77,Default,,0,0,0,,看来他们还是关心舰长的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Then they care about the captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.94,0:12:44.11,Default,,0,0,0,,他们想要他活着回去，长官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They want him back. Alive, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.28,0:12:47.45,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我需要知道为什么 - 如果你耐心点，答案…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- I demand to know why. - If you'll be patient, the answers to--
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.61,0:12:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,,你忘了你是在接受审判，史波克\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You're forgetting you're on trial, Spock.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.95,0:12:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你必须回答所有问题\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You will answer all questions put to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.37,0:12:55.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我的答案让人难以置信，长官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}My answer to your question would be quite unbelievable, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.41,0:12:58.25,Default,,0,0,0,,很遗憾你必须耐心自己去看\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I regret we'll have to wait and see it there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.07,0:13:13.66,Default,,0,0,0,,个人日志，星历3010.2\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Personal log, stardate 3013.2.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.82,0:13:16.95,Default,,0,0,0,,对史波克的军事审判重新开始\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Reconvening court-martial of Mr. Spock
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.12,0:13:22.37,Default,,0,0,0,,星舰上有史以来最奇怪的证物也再次\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and the strangest trial evidence ever heard aboard a starship.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.54,0:13:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,从那颗离我们只有1小时路程的星球传来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}From the mysterious planet now only one hour ahead of us,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.50,0:13:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,关于派克舰长在关押期间的故事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}the story of Captain Pike's imprisonment there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.22,0:13:34.09,Default,,0,0,0,,你为何在此？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.97,0:13:36.18,Default,,0,0,0,,取悦你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}To please you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.60,0:13:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,你是真实的吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Are you real?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.77,0:13:42.14,Default,,0,0,0,,- 跟你想地一样真实 - 噢，不\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- As real as you wish. - Oh, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.85,0:13:45.23,Default,,0,0,0,,不，那不是我要的答案\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No, that's not any answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.27,0:13:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我从未遇到过你，从未想过你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I've never met you before, never even imagined you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.99,0:13:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,,也许他们从你遗忘的梦里找到我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Perhaps they made me out of dreams you've forgotten.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.95,0:13:56.62,Default,,0,0,0,,是么？然后让你穿跟他们一样的金属纤维衣服？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What, and dressed you in the same metal fabric they wear?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.78,0:13:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我可以穿任何你喜欢的衣服\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Or I can wear whatever you wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.33,0:14:01.25,Default,,0,0,0,,变成任何你想要的样子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Be anything you wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.41,0:14:04.96,Default,,0,0,0,,然后他们就可以观察标本的反应？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}So they can see how their specimen performs?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.13,0:14:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,他们想看我如何反应，是吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They want to see how I react, is that it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.75,0:14:10.05,Default,,0,0,0,,你难道就不曾梦过\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Don't you have a dream,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.21,0:14:12.63,Default,,0,0,0,,某件你极其渴望的东西？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}something you've always wanted very badly?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.80,0:14:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,难道他们不仅仅想观察我？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Or do they do more than just watch me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.89,0:14:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,他们…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Do they...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.80,0:14:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,还能感受我的感受？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}...feel with me too?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.76,0:14:22.39,Default,,0,0,0,,你可以拥有任何你想要的东西\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You can have whatever dream you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.56,0:14:24.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我可以成为任何人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I can become anything,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.52,0:14:28.19,Default,,0,0,0,,任何你想要的女人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}any woman you've ever imagined.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.36,0:14:31.99,Default,,0,0,0,,整个宇宙，你想要什么便能拥有什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You can have anything you want in the whole universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.74,0:14:34.28,Default,,0,0,0,,让我…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Let me...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.32,0:14:36.49,Default,,0,0,0,,满足你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}...please you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.45,0:14:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,是的，是，你可以取悦我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yes, yes, you can please me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.24,0:14:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,你可以跟我讲他们的事情\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You can tell me about them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.50,0:14:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,有什么办法可以让我阻止他们看穿我的心思\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Is there any way I can keep them from probing my mind
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.08,0:14:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,阻止他们利用我的思维控制我？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and from using my thoughts against me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.75,0:14:52.71,Default,,0,0,0,,你害怕了？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Does that frighten you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.17,0:14:55.72,Default,,0,0,0,,也就是说有办法？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Does that mean there is a way?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.01,0:14:59.47,Default,,0,0,0,,你是个笨蛋\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You're a fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.01,0:15:01.22,Default,,0,0,0,,既然你不是真实的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And since you're not real,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.39,0:15:03.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我们也没必要再继续聊了，对吧？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}there's not much point in continuing this conversation, is there?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.03,0:15:17.53,Default,,0,0,0,,- 线路安装完毕，史波克先生 - 待命，大副\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- All circuits engaged, Mr. Spock. - Standing by, Number One.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.41,0:15:22.33,Default,,0,0,0,,- 找掩护 - 10、9、8\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Take cover. - Ten, nine, eight,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.00,0:15:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,7、6、5\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}seven, six, five,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.83,0:15:31.54,Default,,0,0,0,,4、3、2、1\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}four, three, two, one.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.56,0:15:49.69,Default,,0,0,0,,增至最大能量！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Increase to full power!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.25,0:16:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,还能再大些吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Can you give us any more?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.93,0:16:21.05,Default,,0,0,0,,电路开始发热了，必须停止火力\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Our circuits are beginning to heat. We'll have to cease power.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.76,0:16:25.47,Default,,0,0,0,,停火！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Disengage!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.28,0:16:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,那个小山包一开始就该被铲平\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The top of that knoll should've been sheared off the first second.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.95,0:16:44.45,Default,,0,0,0,,也许早就被铲平了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Maybe it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.62,0:16:46.95,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是我在简报室想说的事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's what I tried to explain in the briefing room.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.12,0:16:51.33,Default,,0,0,0,,他们制造幻觉的强大精神力量使我们无法确认任何所做之事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Their power of illusion is so great, we can't be sure of anything we do
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.50,0:16:53.79,Default,,0,0,0,,或看见的任何东西\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}or anything we see.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.30,0:17:04.97,Default,,0,0,0,,或许你来问我些问题\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Perhaps if you asked me some questions,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.14,0:17:07.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我能解答\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I could answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.93,0:17:11.89,Default,,0,0,0,,他们能把我的思想控制到什么程度？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}How far can they control my mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.90,0:17:16.23,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我告诉你，你能挑选一个过去的梦\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}If I tell you, then will you pick some dream you've had,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.40,0:17:18.53,Default,,0,0,0,,然后让我跟你一起在里面生活吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and let me live it with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.86,0:17:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,也许吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Perhaps.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.91,0:17:24.45,Default,,0,0,0,,他们不能让你做不愿意做的事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They can't actually make you do anything you don't want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.62,0:17:26.41,Default,,0,0,0,,但他们会用幻觉引诱我去做\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But they try to trick me with their illusions.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.58,0:17:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你抵抗的话，他们还会惩罚你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And they can punish you when you're not cooperative.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.16,0:17:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,你很快就能找到答案\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You'll find out about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.37,0:17:34.33,Default,,0,0,0,,他们曾经在地面上生活过吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Did they ever live on the surface of this planet?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.84,0:17:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,他们为什么来到地下？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Why did they go underground?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.09,0:17:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,战争，几千个世纪以前\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}War. Thousands of centuries ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.42,0:17:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,,地上为何如此贫瘠？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That's why it's so barren up there?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.55,0:17:45.18,Default,,0,0,0,,这个星球才刚恢复适宜生命繁衍的状态\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The planet's only now becoming able to support life again.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.18,0:17:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,所以塔罗斯人到地下之后发现活动范围有限\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}So the Talosians who came underground found life limited here,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.27,0:17:52.23,Default,,0,0,0,,就开始专心发展精神力量\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and they concentrated on developing their mental power.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.39,0:17:55.02,Default,,0,0,0,,他们发现这是个陷阱\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They found it's a trap,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.19,0:17:56.48,Default,,0,0,0,,就像毒品\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}like a narcotic.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.86,0:18:00.99,Default,,0,0,0,,因为当梦比现实更重要的时候\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Because when dreams become more important than reality,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.15,0:18:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,人们不再旅行，建造，发明\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}you give up travel, building, creating.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.03,0:18:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,甚至连怎么修\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You even forget how to repair the machines
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.87,0:18:08.87,Default,,0,0,0,,那些祖先留下的机器都忘了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}left behind by your ancestors.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.04,0:18:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,他们什么都不做，只靠别人的记忆生活\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You just sit, living and reliving other lives
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.37,0:18:15.33,Default,,0,0,0,,虚幻的生活\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}left behind in the thought records.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.50,0:18:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,或者研究一下像我这种“动物标本”的思维\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Or sit probing the minds of zoo specimens like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.50,0:18:21.71,Default,,0,0,0,,对你的观察远不止看戏这么简单，他们为你制造幻觉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You're better than a theatre to them. They create an illusion for you,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.88,0:18:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,看你的反应，体会你的情绪\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}they watch you react, feel your emotions.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.30,0:18:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,他们收集了一整套标本\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They have a whole collection of specimens,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.76,0:18:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,,都是很久以前带回来的生物的后代\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}descendants of life brought back long ago
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.39,0:18:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,来自银河系各个地方\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}from all over this part of the galaxy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.60,0:18:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,也就是说每种生物至少收集一对\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Which means they had to have more than one of each animal.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.94,0:18:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,- 别再说了 - 他们收集的人类也要一对\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Please. - They'll need a pair of humans too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.57,0:18:44.07,Default,,0,0,0,,他们打算去哪儿找那个女的呢？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Where do they intend to get the woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.24,0:18:46.82,Default,,0,0,0,,你说过如果我回答你的问题…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You said that if I answered your questions--
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.99,0:18:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,,但我是在和一个虚幻的东西讨价还价\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But that was a bargain with something that didn't exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.91,0:18:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,你说过你不是真实的，记得吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You said you weren't real, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.17,0:18:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我是个女人…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm a woman...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.75,0:19:02.21,Default,,0,0,0,,跟你一样真实\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}...as real and as human as you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.26,0:19:07.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我们就像亚当和夏娃\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We're like Adam and Eve.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.39,0:19:08.93,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我们…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}If we...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.89,0:19:11.26,Default,,0,0,0,,不要！求你了！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Don't! Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.43,0:19:14.73,Default,,0,0,0,,不要惩罚我！我尽力了！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Don't punish me! I tried!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.29,0:19:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,一个来自地球的女人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}An Earth woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.87,0:19:37.79,Default,,0,0,0,,你被当成种畜抓了起来？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Then you were captured as breeding stock?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.79,0:19:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.30,0:19:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,只为保持动物园里标本的供应吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Just to maintain a supply of zoo specimens?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.88,0:19:46.59,Default,,0,0,0,,远不止此，舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Much more, captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.99,0:20:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,瓶子里是一种营养蛋白复合物\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The vial contains a nourishing protein complex.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.50,0:20:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,动物管理员在跟他养的动物交流？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Is the Keeper actually communicating with one of his animals?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.67,0:20:25.46,Default,,0,0,0,,如果食物的样子和颜色不合适\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}If the form and the colour is not appealing,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.63,0:20:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我可以让它变成你想吃的任何食物\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}it can appear as any food you wish to visualise.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.84,0:20:33.35,Default,,0,0,0,,- 如果我情愿…？ - 饿着？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- And if I prefer--? - To starve?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.51,0:20:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你忘了不合作就会被惩罚\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You overlook the unpleasant alternative of punishment.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.25,0:21:01.83,Default,,0,0,0,,来自你小时候听过的神话故事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}From a fable you once heard in childhood.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.42,0:21:05.38,Default,,0,0,0,,你现在赶紧吃掉营养液\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You will now consume the nourishment.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.38,0:21:11.05,Default,,0,0,0,,为何你不能让我的大脑产生饥饿的念头？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Why not just put irresistible hunger in my mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.39,0:21:13.01,Default,,0,0,0,,因为你不能，是吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Because you can't, can you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.18,0:21:14.97,Default,,0,0,0,,你能力的确有限，是吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You do have limitations, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.14,0:21:17.22,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你再不听话\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}If you continue to disobey,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.39,0:21:19.23,Default,,0,0,0,,在你的脑海里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}from deeper in your mind,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.39,0:21:22.31,Default,,0,0,0,,还有让你更痛苦的事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}there are things even more unpleasant.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.92,0:21:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,真有意思\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That's very interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.71,0:21:46.21,Default,,0,0,0,,现在说说那个女的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Now to the female.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.38,0:21:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,你刚才被吓到了，你不是会读心术吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You were startled. Weren't you reading my mind then?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.09,0:21:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,如你猜测的那样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}As you've conjectured,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.55,0:21:55.09,Default,,0,0,0,,一艘地球飞船在我们的星球上坠毁，只有一个幸存者\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}an Earth vessel did crash on our planet, but with only a single survivor.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.26,0:21:57.22,Default,,0,0,0,,现在，回到之前的话题\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Now, let's stay on the first subject.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.39,0:22:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我当时想用双手掐住你的脖子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}All I wanted for that moment was to get my hands around your neck.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.77,0:22:02.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我们治好了幸存者的伤\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We repaired the survivor's injuries,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.02,0:22:05.19,Default,,0,0,0,,发现这种生物很有意思\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and found the species interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.36,0:22:07.77,Default,,0,0,0,,是不是原始的思绪能阻止你洞察人心？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Do primitive thoughts put up a block you can't read through?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.94,0:22:10.57,Default,,0,0,0,,这变成必须要吸引一个男性\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It became necessary to attract a mate.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.74,0:22:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧，好吧，我们就聊聊那个女孩\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}All right, all right, let's talk about the girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.91,0:22:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你似乎煞费了苦心让她变得魅力十足\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You seem to be going out of your way to make her attractive,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.37,0:22:18.91,Default,,0,0,0,,想让我因此产生保护的欲望\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}to make me feel protective.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.08,0:22:22.29,Default,,0,0,0,,为了保持物种繁衍，必须这样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}This is necessary in order to perpetuate the species.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.00,0:22:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我接受她喜欢她似乎对你更重要\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It seems more important to you now that I begin to accept her and like her.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.21,0:22:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我们希望我们的标本能在这儿过得开心\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We wish our specimens to be happy in their new life.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.34,0:22:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,假设这是个谎言\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Assuming that's a lie,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.47,0:22:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,你为什么想我喜欢她？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}why would you want me attracted to her?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.80,0:22:40.93,Default,,0,0,0,,这样我才能体会夫妻间的那种爱？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}So I'll feel love in a husband-wife relationship?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.10,0:22:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,除非想成家，才会这样做\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That'd be necessary only if you intend to build a family group,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.81,0:22:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,,整个人类社会都是这样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}or perhaps a whole human community.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.48,0:22:50.82,Default,,0,0,0,,- 在雌性被适当处理的情况下 - 你是说适当惩罚的情况下！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- With the female properly conditioned. - You mean properly punished!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.32,0:22:54.99,Default,,0,0,0,,是我不听话，你为什么不惩罚我？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm the one who's not cooperating. Why don't you punish me?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.82,0:22:59.41,Default,,0,0,0,,先是情感的防范\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}First, an emotional protectiveness.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.58,0:23:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,现在又是同情\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Now, one of sympathy.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.66,0:23:04.25,Default,,0,0,0,,很好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Excellent.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.34,0:23:15.30,Default,,0,0,0,,亲爱的，来点咖啡？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You want some coffee, dear?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.73,0:23:27.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我把热水瓶挂在马鞍上了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I left the Thermos hooked to my saddle.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.37,0:23:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,探戈\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Tango.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.54,0:23:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,你这个老家伙\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You old devil, you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.38,0:23:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉，我身上没带…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm sorry, I don't have any s--
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.26,0:23:56.01,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧，他们考虑得还真周到\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Well, they think of everything, don't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.55,0:24:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,- 回到家感觉很棒吧？ - 他们真算得上“脑子”里的蛔虫\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Is it good to be home? - They read our minds very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.31,0:24:05.56,Default,,0,0,0,,家，还有我想要的任何东西\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Home, anything else I want,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.73,0:24:07.31,Default,,0,0,0,,前提是我合作，是吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}if I cooperate, is that it?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.48,0:24:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,天啊，这还真是美好的一天，不是吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}My, it turned out to be a lovely day, didn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.69,0:24:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,你回家了，甚至可以留在家里，如果你愿意\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You're home. You can even stay, if you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.41,0:24:20.41,Default,,0,0,0,,但是，我们俩并不在这儿\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But we're not here, neither of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.57,0:24:23.74,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我们只是在一个动物园的笼子里 - 不要！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- We're in a menagerie, a cage. - No!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.91,0:24:26.41,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你不给我机会的话，我谁都帮不了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I can't help either one of us if you won't give me a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.58,0:24:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你告诉过我，他们把幻觉当麻醉剂\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You told me once they used illusions as a narcotic.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.25,0:24:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,他们甚至不能修好祖先留下来的机器\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They couldn't even repair the machines left by their ancestors.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.17,0:24:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是他们需要我们的原因吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Is that why they want us?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.76,0:24:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,- 来建立一个满是奴隶的殖民地？ - 别说了！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- To build a colony of slaves? - Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.38,0:24:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,,难道你不关心他们会怎么对我们吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Don't you care what they'll do to us?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.26,0:24:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,在笼子里的时候，好像有那么几分钟\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Back in my cage, it seemed for a couple of minutes
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.43,0:24:46.27,Default,,0,0,0,,“饲养员”不能读取我的心思\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}that our keeper couldn't read my thoughts.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.64,0:24:50.69,Default,,0,0,0,,像仇恨那样的感情，在脑海中集中起仇恨\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Do emotions like hate, keeping hate in your mind,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.02,0:24:52.94,Default,,0,0,0,,这样他们的读心术就不会奏效了？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}does that block off our mind from them?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.82,0:25:01.61,Default,,0,0,0,,对，他们无法读取原始情感\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yes. They can't read through primitive emotions.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.78,0:25:05.95,Default,,0,0,0,,但是你不能坚持足够久的，我试过了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But you can't keep it up for long enough. I’ve tried.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.41,0:25:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,他们就年复一年地纠缠你，戏弄你，惩罚你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They keep at you and at you, year after year, tricking you, punishing.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.83,0:25:13.67,Default,,0,0,0,,他们就赢了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And they won.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.17,0:25:16.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我现在是他们的了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They own me.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.38,0:25:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,,你肯定会因此而讨厌我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I know you must hate me for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.14,0:25:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,不，我并不讨厌你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Oh, no, I don't hate you.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.39,0:25:27.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我能想到那是怎样的经历\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I can guess what it was like.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.14,0:25:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,这还不是全部\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That's not enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.27,0:25:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,难道你没有发现吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Don't you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.19,0:25:36.69,Default,,0,0,0,,他们读取我的心思，我的感受\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They read my thoughts, my feelings,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.86,0:25:40.90,Default,,0,0,0,,还有我梦中的白马王子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}my dreams of what would be the perfect man.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.65,0:25:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是他们选择你的原因\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That's why they picked you.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.33,0:25:47.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我不得不爱你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I can't help but love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.33,0:25:51.83,Default,,0,0,0,,他们也期待你和我有同样的感受\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And they expect you to feel the same way.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.54,0:25:56.59,Default,,0,0,0,,如果他们能读取我的心思，他们就会知道我被你深深吸引着\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}If they can read my mind, then they know I’m attracted to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.00,0:26:00.51,Default,,0,0,0,,从在幸存者营地看见你的第一眼起\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I was from the very first moment I saw you in the survivor's camp.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.01,0:26:04.26,Default,,0,0,0,,你就像个狂野的小动物\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You were like a wild little animal.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.30,0:26:08.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我终于开始明白为什么这些对你都没用了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm beginning to see why none of this has worked for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.52,0:26:12.39,Default,,0,0,0,,在家里，在参宿七战斗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You've been home and fighting, as on Rigel.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.56,0:26:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,这些对你都不陌生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That's not new to you either.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.77,0:26:19.53,Default,,0,0,0,,而得不到的永远在骚动\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}A person's strongest dreams are about what he can't do.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.69,0:26:22.03,Default,,0,0,0,,是的，对于一位舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yes, a ship's captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.20,0:26:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,总是得正式\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Always having to be so formal,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.86,0:26:27.45,Default,,0,0,0,,得体、可靠、礼仪周全\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}so decent and honest and proper.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.62,0:26:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你一定很想知道，没有这些束缚是什么样子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You must wonder what it would be like to forget all that.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.81,0:26:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,美妙的地方，派克先生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Nice place you have here, Mr. Pike.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.74,0:27:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,维娜？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Vina?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.54,0:27:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,那又是维娜？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That's Vina again?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.37,0:27:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,变成了绿色的猎户座女奴？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}As the green Orion slave girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.50,0:27:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,她们就像野兽，堕落又迷人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They're like animals. Vicious, seductive.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.00,0:27:24.01,Default,,0,0,0,,她们说没有人类的男性能抵挡住其诱惑\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They say no human male can resist them.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.44,0:27:44.86,Default,,0,0,0,,来自过去的奇怪证据\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Strange evidence from the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.13,0:27:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,为了繁育一个把人类当奴隶的社会\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}How the Talosians, planning to breed a society of human slaves,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.10,0:27:52.77,Default,,0,0,0,,塔罗斯人用他们囚禁的地球女子引诱派克舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}tempted Captain Pike with the Earth woman they held in captivity.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.94,0:27:54.77,Default,,0,0,0,,她以多种面貌出现在他面前\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And as she appeared to him in many forms,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.84,0:27:57.22,Default,,0,0,0,,一次比一次性感\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}each more exciting than the last,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.43,0:27:59.59,Default,,0,0,0,,派克开始动摇了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Pike was beginning to weaken.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.12,0:28:20.16,Default,,0,0,0,,设想你的选择千千万万\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Suppose you had all of space to choose from,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.33,0:28:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,而这只是一个小小的样本\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and this was only one small sample.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.59,0:28:26.55,Default,,0,0,0,,难道你不觉得这值得一个男人出卖其灵魂吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Wouldn't you say it was worth a man's soul?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.48,0:29:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,你们都知道现在的状况了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Well, you all know the situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.65,0:29:34.07,Default,,0,0,0,,希望我们能直接传送到塔罗斯人的地盘里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We're hoping to transport down inside the Talosian community.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.24,0:29:37.24,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我们的测量读数也是幻觉的话\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}If our measurements and readings are an illusion also,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.41,0:29:40.29,Default,,0,0,0,,你可能会发现自己出现在一块坚石里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}one could find oneself materialized inside solid rock.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.45,0:29:43.87,Default,,0,0,0,,如果谁想退出，没人会责怪的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Nothing will be said if any volunteer wants to back out.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.56,0:30:03.06,Default,,0,0,0,,女人！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The women!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.03,0:30:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,,舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.62,0:30:21.33,Default,,0,0,0,,舰长？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Captain?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.91,0:30:24.91,Default,,0,0,0,,不要！让我做完呀！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No! Let me finish!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.04,0:30:30.09,Default,,0,0,0,,但我们是一行六人才对，只有我们被传送过来了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But we were a party of six. We were the only ones transported.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.25,0:30:33.05,Default,,0,0,0,,这不公平，你不需要她们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's not fair. You don't need them.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.71,0:30:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,用不了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They don't work.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.09,0:30:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我们出发时能量可是充满的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They were fully charged when we left.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.43,0:30:47.72,Default,,0,0,0,,没用，发不出信号\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's dead. I can't make a signal.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.25,0:30:51.30,Default,,0,0,0,,- 这是怎么回事？ - 别说话\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- What is it? - Don't say anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.30,0:30:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,现在我的脑海中是一幅把他们畸形的大脑袋打成肉酱的画面\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm filling my mind with a picture of beating their misshapen heads to pulp,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.18,0:31:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,,原始情感，这样他们就把一切都中断了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}thoughts so primitive they black out everything else.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.98,0:31:03.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我在脑海里积聚着仇恨\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm filling my mind with hate.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.15,0:31:05.85,Default,,0,0,0,,你能把思想阻滞多久？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}How long can you block your thoughts?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.02,0:31:07.82,Default,,0,0,0,,几分钟？一小时？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}A few minutes? An hour?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.08,0:31:11.29,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你觉得有用吗？ - 别打扰他\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- How can that help? - Leave him alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.75,0:31:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,他不需要你，他已经选择了我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He doesn't need you. He's already picked me.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.09,0:31:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,选择了她？为什么？我不懂\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Picked her? For what? I don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.97,0:31:22.26,Default,,0,0,0,,为了高智商后代，他真应该选你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Now there's a fine choice for intelligent offspring.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.43,0:31:24.77,Default,,0,0,0,,后代？孩子吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Offspring? As in children?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.10,0:31:28.77,Default,,0,0,0,,后代就是说，他是亚当，对吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Offspring as in, he's Adam. Is that it?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.44,0:31:30.73,Default,,0,0,0,,你也没有好多少\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You're no better choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.90,0:31:33.86,Default,,0,0,0,,他们还不如让他和电脑在一起\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They'd have more luck crossing him with a computer.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.61,0:31:37.82,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧，要不我们来做个简单的计算题？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Well, shall we do a little time-computation?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.99,0:31:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,那时的探险队名单上有个叫维娜的成年女子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}There was a Vina listed on that expedition as an adult crewman.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.87,0:31:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,现在，我们加上18年，就会…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Now, adding 18 years to your age then...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.46,0:31:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,这不公平！我照你的要求做了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's not fair! I did what you asked.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.80,0:31:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,既然你拒绝了之前的样本\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Since you resist the present specimen,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.30,0:31:59.88,Default,,0,0,0,,你现在多了几个选择\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}you now have a selection.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.05,0:32:03.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我总会突破这笼子来到你面前的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'll break out of this zoo somehow and get to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.06,0:32:07.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我倒要看看你的血是不是和我们的一样红\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Is your blood red like ours? I'm gonna find out.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.98,0:32:12.02,Default,,0,0,0,,这两个新样本有她们各自的优点\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Each of the two new specimens has qualities in her favour.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.19,0:32:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,这位你称之为“大副”的女性头脑更出众\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The female you call "Number One" has the superior mind,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.48,0:32:17.99,Default,,0,0,0,,会产出高智商的后代\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and would produce highly intelligent children.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.15,0:32:21.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我唯一想做的就是亲手捉到你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}All I want to do is get my hands on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.41,0:32:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,,你能读到这些想法吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Can you read these thoughts:
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.49,0:32:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,仇恨杀戮的画面？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Images of hate, killing?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.83,0:32:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,另一个新来的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The other new arrival
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.50,0:32:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,一直以为你遥不可及，但现在意识到了转机\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}has considered you unreachable, but now is realising this has changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.46,0:32:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,她的优势是青春活力\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The factors in her favour are youth and strength,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.38,0:32:39.09,Default,,0,0,0,,加上异常强烈的女性魅力\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}plus unusually strong female drives.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.51,0:32:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你会发现我的思想更有意思\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You'll find my thoughts more interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.26,0:32:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,你不懂的原始情感\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Thoughts so primitive you can't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.89,0:32:46.51,Default,,0,0,0,,丑恶的情感…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Emotions so ugly--
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.48,0:32:54.77,Default,,0,0,0,,错误的思想会自食苦果\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Wrong thinking is punishable.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.94,0:32:58.19,Default,,0,0,0,,正确的思想会即刻得到奖励\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Right thinking will be as quickly rewarded.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.36,0:33:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你会发现这是个有效的组合\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You will find it an effective combination.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.21,0:33:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,- 舰长… - 不，不用管我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Captain-- - No, no, don't help me.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.25,0:33:17.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我必须得集中精力\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I have to concentrate.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.71,0:33:19.59,Default,,0,0,0,,他们不能读透仇恨\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They can't read through hate.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.50,0:34:01.09,Default,,0,0,0,,- 老实点，否则我… - 别伤害他\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Hold still or I'll-- - Don't hurt him.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.26,0:34:02.76,Default,,0,0,0,,他们并不是坏人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They don't mean to be evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.92,0:34:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,他们多么善良我可是如数家珍\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I've had some samples of how good they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.73,0:34:20.61,Default,,0,0,0,,把这幻觉停下，否则我直接把你脑袋拧下来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You stop this illusion or I'll twist your head off.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.41,0:34:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,好了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.54,0:34:32.66,Default,,0,0,0,,你要是再尝试新的幻觉，哪怕丁点半点\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Now, you try one more illusion, you try anything at all,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.83,0:34:34.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我就拧断你的脖子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and I'll break your neck.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.46,0:34:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你的星舰\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Your ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.92,0:34:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,放开我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Release me...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.63,0:34:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,否则我们就毁了它\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}...or we'll destroy it.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.22,0:34:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,,他没有虚张声势，舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He's not bluffing, captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.80,0:34:50.35,Default,,0,0,0,,利用幻觉，他们会让你的船员出现误操作\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}With illusion, they can make your crew work the wrong controls
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.51,0:34:53.97,Default,,0,0,0,,或者按下某个按钮，只要能毁掉你的舰船\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}or push any button it takes to destroy your ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.35,0:34:59.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我打赌你们这么智慧的生物不会毫无理由地杀戮\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm gonna gamble you're too intelligent to kill for no reason at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.33,0:35:16.33,Default,,0,0,0,,不过，我这里有个理由了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}On the other hand, I've got a reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.50,0:35:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我打赌你又创造了一个激光枪没有能量的幻觉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm willing to bet you've created an illusion this laser is empty.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.17,0:35:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得刚才那个窗户已经被打出了一个洞\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I think it just blasted a hole in that window
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.21,0:35:24.17,Default,,0,0,0,,你在从中作梗让我们看不见\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and you're keeping us from seeing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.34,0:35:26.67,Default,,0,0,0,,你是不是要我在你的脑袋上检验我的理论呢？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You want me to test my theory out on your head?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.39,0:35:31.14,Default,,0,0,0,,舰长！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.71,0:36:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,看来塔罗斯人抛弃了你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It seems the Talosians have deserted you.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.71,0:36:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,先生们，请稍等一会\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Gentlemen, a moment, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.88,0:36:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,史波克？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Well, Mr. Spock?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.39,0:36:18.31,Default,,0,0,0,,- 您有裁决了吗？ - 是您希望他们停止讯号的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- May I have your verdict? - Signal you want them to wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.44,0:36:24.65,Default,,0,0,0,,舰长，拜托了，这关系到您的生命，至少给生命一次机会\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Captain, please. It's your life now. At least a chance for life.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.82,0:36:28.15,Default,,0,0,0,,史波克，你总是在谈生命，给生命一次机会\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You keep talking about life, Mr. Spock, a chance for life.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:28.32,0:36:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,怎样的生命？当一个囚徒？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}How? As a prisoner?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.07,0:36:33.87,Default,,0,0,0,,关在笼子里？当一个动物园的标本？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Caged? A zoo specimen?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.03,0:36:36.37,Default,,0,0,0,,在幻觉中生活，以取悦他的管理员？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Living the illusions that amuse his keepers?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.54,0:36:38.45,Default,,0,0,0,,不，舰长，不仅仅只有这么多\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No, captain. There's more to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.62,0:36:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,看吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.05,0:36:47.84,Default,,0,0,0,,有罪？是或否，舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Guilty? Yes or no, captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.30,0:36:54.89,Default,,0,0,0,,有罪\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.47,0:36:58.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我必须也投“罪名成立”\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I must also vote "guilty as charged."
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.94,0:37:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,,你呢，舰长？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And you, captain?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.11,0:37:11.78,Default,,0,0,0,,罪名…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Guilty...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.95,0:37:13.11,Default,,0,0,0,,成立\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}...as charged.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.96,0:37:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,舰桥呼叫指挥官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Bridge to commander.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.09,0:37:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,- 这里是门德兹 - 长官，我们正在进入塔罗斯四号的轨道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Mendez here. - Sir, we're entering orbit, Talos IV.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.47,0:37:40.39,Default,,0,0,0,,长官，塔罗斯现在控制着这艘舰船，就像他们十三年前一样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Talos controls the vessel now, sir, as they did 13 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.56,0:37:44.81,Default,,0,0,0,,你们问过我原因，现在你们就能看到答案\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You've asked me why. You'll see the answer now.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.96,0:38:11.01,Default,,0,0,0,,取得联络，大副\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Make contact, Number One.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.17,0:38:13.09,Default,,0,0,0,,他们也不让我们看到这个\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They kept us from seeing this too.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.26,0:38:15.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我们接通了却根本不知道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We cut through and never knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.01,0:38:18.81,Default,,0,0,0,,舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.73,0:38:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,你也看到了，你想出逃的努力毫无结果\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}As you see, your attempt to escape accomplished nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:27.52,0:38:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我想联络我的舰船\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I want to contact our ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:28.98,0:38:33.03,Default,,0,0,0,,你现在就在星球表面，也就是我们希望你生活的地方\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You are now on the surface, where we wished you to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:33.65,0:38:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,和你选择的女性一起\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}With the female of your choice,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.49,0:38:39.87,Default,,0,0,0,,你现在可以开始精心规划好的生活\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}you will now begin carefully guided lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:40.04,0:38:41.79,Default,,0,0,0,,就从把你埋葬开始吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And start by burying you?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.54,0:38:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,那是你自己的选择\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That is your choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.37,0:38:47.79,Default,,0,0,0,,为了帮助你重新开垦这星球表面\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}To help you reclaim the planet surface,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.96,0:38:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,动物园会提供各种各样的植物生命\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}our zoological gardens will furnish a variety of plant life.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.05,0:38:54.13,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧，我和你来做个交易\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Look, I'll make a deal with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.30,0:38:57.22,Default,,0,0,0,,你的命换这两位地球女性的生命\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You and your life for the lives of these two Earth women.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.35,0:39:01.89,Default,,0,0,0,,你证明我的舰船完好无损，把她们俩送回去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You give me proof that our ship is all right, send these two back,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:02.06,0:39:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我就会和维娜留下来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and I'll stay with Vina.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.98,0:39:13.99,Default,,0,0,0,,创造一整个奴隶般生活的人类种族是错误的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's wrong to create a whole race of humans to live as slaves.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:15.28,0:39:17.41,Default,,0,0,0,,这是一个骗局吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Is this a deception?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.57,0:39:20.41,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你想自我毁灭吗？ - 这是怎么回事？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Do you intend to destroy yourselves? - What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.58,0:39:23.41,Default,,0,0,0,,这武器会累积到过载，带来强力的爆炸\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The weapon is building up an overload, a force chamber explosion.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.08,0:39:27.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你还有时间回到地下去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You still have time to get underground.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.58,0:39:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,好了，快走吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Well, go on!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.92,0:39:37.59,Default,,0,0,0,,就给你看看人类有多么原始，塔罗斯人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Just to show you how primitive humans are, Talosian...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.89,0:39:40.85,Default,,0,0,0,,你和她一起走\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}...you go with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.43,0:39:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你们觉得这如此重要\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}If... If you all think it's this important,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.77,0:39:47.27,Default,,0,0,0,,那么我也不能走\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}then I can't go either.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.73,0:39:51.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得如果他们有一个人类，就可能会再次尝试\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I suppose if they have one human being, they might try again.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.45,0:39:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,等等\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.62,0:40:06.45,Default,,0,0,0,,他们存储记录的技术很粗糙，花了很多时间\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Their method of storing records is crude and consumed much time.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.62,0:40:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你准备好吸收了吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Are you prepared to assimilate it?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.81,0:40:27.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我们一直以为这不可能\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We had not believed this possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.10,0:40:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,你们种族的习俗和历史表明你们对奴役的仇恨是独一无二的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The customs and history of your race show a unique hatred of captivity.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:34.98,0:40:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,即使安逸舒适\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Even when it's pleasant and benevolent,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.28,0:40:39.82,Default,,0,0,0,,你们却宁死不从\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}you prefer death.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:40.36,0:40:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,,对我们的需求来说，你们这个物种太凶暴，太危险了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}This makes you too violent and dangerous a species for our needs.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.54,0:40:48.87,Default,,0,0,0,,他的意思是他不能用你了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He means that they can't use you.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.04,0:40:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你现在可以自由地回到舰船了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You're free to go back to the ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.59,0:40:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,就这样了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And that's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:58.05,0:40:59.97,Default,,0,0,0,,连句道歉都没有\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No apologies.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.47,0:41:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你们俘虏了一个人，却威胁了我们所有人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You captured one of us, threatened all of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.97,0:41:08.52,Default,,0,0,0,,你的不相称已经宣告了塔罗斯族的死刑\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Your unsuitability has condemned the Talosian race to eventual death.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:08.85,0:41:10.64,Default,,0,0,0,,这还不够吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Is this not sufficient?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.81,0:41:14.27,Default,,0,0,0,,没有其他样本展示了你这样的适应能力\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No other specimen has shown your adaptability.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.69,0:41:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,你是我们最后的希望\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You were our last hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.61,0:41:20.19,Default,,0,0,0,,但不会是某种形式的交易\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But wouldn't some form of trade,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:20.78,0:41:22.11,Default,,0,0,0,,互助合作…？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}mutual cooperation...?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.78,0:41:27.33,Default,,0,0,0,,你们的种族也会习得我们制造幻觉的能力，并最终自我毁灭\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Your race would learn our power of illusion and destroy itself too.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:28.20,0:41:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,,舰长，我们有传送器信号了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Captain, we have transporter control now.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:38.67,0:41:40.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我们回舰上去吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Let's get back to the ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:46.18,0:41:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我不能\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.77,0:41:49.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我不能和你们一起走\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I can't go with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:49.77,0:41:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,长官，它自动启动了，没办法停下\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Sir, it just came on. We can't shut the power off.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:52.73,0:41:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,- 这里是史波克 - 所有能量都启动了，史波克\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Mr. Spock here. - All power's come on, Mr. Spock.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:55.56,0:41:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,船舵正在回应控制\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The helm is answering to control.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:24.59,0:42:26.01,Default,,0,0,0,,舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:02.17,0:43:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,你明白我为何不能跟你一起走了吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You see why I can't go with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:05.97,0:43:08.64,Default,,0,0,0,,这才是这位女性的真实面貌\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}This is the female's true appearance.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:10.56,0:43:14.64,Default,,0,0,0,,他们在残骸里发现了我，奄奄一息\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They found me in the wreckage, dying,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:14.81,0:43:16.89,Default,,0,0,0,,只是一坨肉而已\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}a lump of flesh.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:17.98,0:43:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,他们改造了我，一切正常\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They rebuilt me. Everything works.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:21.61,0:43:24.99,Default,,0,0,0,,但是他们从来没有见过人类\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But they had never seen a human.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:25.61,0:43:30.62,Default,,0,0,0,,他们不知道怎么把我复原\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They had no guide for putting me back together.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:46.84,0:43:51.01,Default,,0,0,0,,很有必要让你确信，她想留下的决定是诚实的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It was necessary to convince you her desire to stay is an honest one.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:51.18,0:43:53.35,Default,,0,0,0,,你会再次给她美貌的幻觉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You'll give her back her illusion of beauty.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:54.35,0:43:56.27,Default,,0,0,0,,不仅如此\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And more.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:12.63,0:44:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,史波克，系统又启动了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Mr. Spock, the system is coming on again.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:35.32,0:44:38.02,Default,,0,0,0,,- 维娜呢？ - 她不和我们一起走吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- What's happened to Vina? - Isn't she coming with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:38.08,0:44:39.24,Default,,0,0,0,,不了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:40.36,0:44:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,而且我认同她的理由\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No, and l agreed with her reasons.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:51.46,0:44:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,- 所有甲板人员准备超空间飞行 - 所有甲板人员准备好了，长官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- All decks prepare for hyperdrive. - All decks are ready, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:56.90,0:44:58.77,Default,,0,0,0,,出发\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Engage.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:29.18,0:45:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,准将，你不认为…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Commodore, don't you think that...?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:42.98,0:45:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,,寇克舰长，你现在听到的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What you now seem to hear, Captain Kirk,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:46.28,0:45:48.53,Default,,0,0,0,,是我的思维传输\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}are my thought transmissions.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:48.86,0:45:51.70,Default,,0,0,0,,准将从来没有登上你的舰船\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The commodore was never aboard your vessel.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:51.87,0:45:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,他的存在只是幻觉，不管是那里还是在穿梭机上\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}His presence there and in the shuttlecraft was an illusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:56.71,0:46:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,史波克先生已经告知我们你强大的意志力\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Mr. Spock had related to us your strength of will.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:01.14,0:46:04.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我们认为，虚构一个军事法庭审判\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It was thought the fiction of a court-martial
Dialogue: 0,0:46:04.19,0:46:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,会转移你的注意力，以免你很快重新掌控舰船\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}would divert you from too soon regaining control of your vessel.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:08.98,0:46:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我们很欢迎派克舰长和我们共度余生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Captain Pike is welcome to spend the rest of his life with us,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:13.86,0:46:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,从他那副躯壳中解脱\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}unfettered by his physical body.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:16.87,0:46:21.66,Default,,0,0,0,,这是你们的，也是他的决定\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The decision is yours and his.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:35.34,0:46:38.68,Default,,0,0,0,,史波克，即使条例很明晰\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Mr. Spock, even if regulations are explicit,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:38.85,0:46:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,你还是可以来我这里解释清楚\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}you could've come to me and explained.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:41.35,0:46:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,请你也来面对极刑？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Ask you to face the death penalty too?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:45.23,0:46:46.69,Default,,0,0,0,,一个人就够了，舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}One of us was enough, captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:49.78,0:46:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,- 是的 - 长官，来自星际基地11号的信息\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Yes. - Message from starbase 11, sir:
Dialogue: 0,0:46:53.57,0:46:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,“收到了来自塔罗斯四号星球的影像\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}"Received images from Talos IV.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:56.37,0:47:00.70,Default,,0,0,0,,鉴于派克舰长在太空探索中的历史重要性\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}In view of historic importance of Captain Pike in space exploration,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:00.87,0:47:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,一般手则第七条，即禁止与塔罗斯四号星接触\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}General Order 7, prohibiting contact Talos IV,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:04.62,0:47:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,在这种情况下暂时失效\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}is suspended this occasion.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:06.29,0:47:08.46,Default,,0,0,0,,针对史波克的行动没有任何诉讼\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No action contemplated against Spock.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:08.63,0:47:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,请酌情妥善处理”\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Proceed as you think best."
Dialogue: 0,0:47:10.17,0:47:14.97,Default,,0,0,0,,署名，门德兹，准将，星际基地11号\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Signed, Mendez, J. I., commodore, Starbase 11.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:25.31,0:47:26.73,Default,,0,0,0,,克里斯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Chris...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:27.56,0:47:29.19,Default,,0,0,0,,你想去吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}...do you want to go there?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:34.07,0:47:35.90,Default,,0,0,0,,史波克\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Mr. Spock...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:36.57,0:47:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,你可以把派克舰长带到传送室吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}...would you care to take Captain Pike to the transporter room?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:42.66,0:47:44.41,Default,,0,0,0,,为他送行\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}See him off.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:45.37,0:47:47.12,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢您，长官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Thank you, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:47.29,0:47:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,代表我们俩\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}For both of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:55.42,0:47:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,史波克，完事之后\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Mr. Spock, when you're finished,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:57.93,0:47:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,请回来见我，我想和你谈谈\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}please come back and see me. I wanna talk to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:59.93,0:48:02.81,Default,,0,0,0,,你最近展现出的令人遗憾的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}This regrettable tendency you've been showing lately
Dialogue: 0,0:48:02.97,0:48:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,公然的情绪化倾向\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}towards flagrant emotionalism...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:04.77,0:48:07.14,Default,,0,0,0,,长官，没有理由去侮辱我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I see no reason to insult me, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:07.31,0:48:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我相信我在整件事中都是完全合符逻辑的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I believe I’ve been completely logical about the whole affair.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:17.78,0:48:19.91,Default,,0,0,0,,寇克舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Captain Kirk.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:46.31,0:48:49.56,Default,,0,0,0,,派克舰长拥有幻想\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Captain Pike has an illusion,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:49.73,0:48:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,你则拥有现实\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and you have reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:52.23,0:48:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,愿你旅途愉快！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}May you find your way as pleasant.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:02.33,0:49:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,本集结束
Dialogue: 0,0:49:12.92,0:49:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,-=The Last Fantasy=-\N谢谢观赏
